      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was looking at the stars tonight and it just hit me. everything we do, every single thing. it's all just noise. in a few billion years the sun dies and everything just goes dark anyway. so what is the point of even trying to exist? it feels like we're just actors in a play that has no audience and no meaning.",
